'''Anfa''' neɣ '''Tigmmi Tumlilt''' ( s [[tifinaɣ]] : '''ⴰⵏⴼⴰ''' neɣ '''ⵜⵉⴳⵎⵎⵉ ⵜⵓⵎⵍⵉⵍⵜ''' ,  s [[Tafrensist|tafransist]] d tulayin tiyaḍ : " Casablanca " , s tutlayt n [[Taɛṛabt|taɛrabt]]: "الدار البيضاء " ''Al-dar Al-bayḍaa'' ) Iɣrem d ameqqran akw di tmurt n [[Merruk|Umerruk]], tili deg yiwen arky (3.269.962 h). D iɣrem d ameqqran akk deg tmazɣa akwd Ledzayer Tamanaɣt.

Tella g '''Anfa''' yiwet timzgida tameqqrant ism-es [[Timzgida Ḥassan II]] .

Ar neqqar imezdaɣen n '''Anfa''' ''"'' ''Bidawa "'' s [[Taɛṛabt|taɛrabt]] , d ''" Casawi "'' s [[darija]] d [[Tamaziɣt (Amerruk)|tamaziɣt]] .

